msgstr "Otrok invalidne osebe v oskrbi šteje kot dva."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1223
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1543
