msgstr "Če je prag zneska presežen, znižanje ne bo odobreno."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1292
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1612
