#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:126
msgid ""
"End of service (EOS) provides the calculation for the allowance that the "
"employee gets at the end of their service. It is triggered when the "
"employee's departure reason is set by archiving the employee's record."
msgstr ""
"Odpravnina ob koncu službe (EOS) izračuna nadomestilo, ki ga kader prejme ob "
"koncu zaposlitve. Sproži se, ko je razlog za odhod kadra nastavljen z "
"arhiviranjem kadrovskega zapisa."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:130
msgid "There are several different calculations depending on the scenario:"
msgstr "Glede na scenarij obstaja več različnih izračunov:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:132
msgid ""
"*The Employee spent less than a year in the company*: The employee does not "
"get any |EOS| allowance since they are not eligible for it (they are "
"eligible once they complete their first year in the company)."
msgstr ""
"*Zaposleni je v podjetju preživel manj kot eno leto*: Zaposleni ne prejme "
"nobene |EOS| odpravnine, saj zanjo ni upravičen (upravičenost je pogojena z "
"vsaj enim letom v podjetju)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:135
msgid ""
"*The Employee spent more than a year and less than 5 years in the company*: "
"The employee is eligible for an equivalent of **21** days of salary for each "
"year they spent on the company."
msgstr ""
"*Kader je v podjetju preživel več kot eno leto in manj kot 5 let*: Kader je "
"upravičen do nadomestila v višini **21** dni plače za vsako leto, ki ga je "
"preživel v podjetju."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:139
msgid ""
"There are two ways for calculating the daily wage that gets paid for the "
"employee against the 21 days of the |EOS|: Either by the default way of "
"dividing the monthly basic wage by 30. Or, it can be manually input on the "
"contract of the employee under the *Daily Salary* field."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata dva načina za izračun dnevne plače, ki se izplača kadru za 21 dni |"
"EOS|: Bodisi s privzetim načinom, ki deli mesečno osnovno plačo s 30, bodisi "
"z ročnim vnosom v pogodbo kadra v polje *Dnevna plača*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:143
msgid ""
"*The Employee spent more than 5 years in the company*: The employee is "
"eligible for an equivalent of **30** days of salary for each year they spent "
"on the company. In this case, if the default method is used, then the "
"employee gets paid an equivalent of 1 month of salary, and the set *Daily "
"Salary* field, they will get the amount for the day multiplied by 30."
msgstr ""
"*Kader je v podjetju preživel več kot 5 let*: Kader je upravičen do "
"nadomestila v višini **30** dni plače za vsako leto, ki ga je preživel v "
"podjetju. V tem primeru, če se uporabi privzeta metoda, kader prejme "
"nadomestilo v višini 1 meseca plače, pri nastavljenem polju *Dnevna plača* "
"pa bo prejel znesek za dan, pomnoženega s 30."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:149
msgid ""
"There are two payslips printout formats, one for normal salaries and one for "
"end of service payslips, it is based on the employee being archived and "
"having a departure reason or not."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata dve obliki izpisa plačilnih list, ena za običajne plače in ena za "
"plačilne liste ob koncu službe, odvisno od tega, ali je kader arhiviran in "
"ima razlog za odhod ali ne."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:153
msgid "End of service provision (EOS Provision)"
msgstr "Rezervacija za konec zagotavljanja storitev (EOS rezervacija)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:155
msgid ""
"The |EOS| provision provides the calculation for the end-of-service "
"provision amount that the company puts aside every month to count for the |"
"EOS| that will be paid to them as an |EOS| allowance."
msgstr ""
"Rezervacija |EOS| zagotavlja izračun zneska rezervacije za konec storitve, "
"ki ga podjetje mesečno odloži za |EOS|, ki bo izplačan zaposlenim kot |EOS| "
"nadomestilo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:159
msgid ""
"Unlike the |EOS|, the provision is part of the employee's payslip from the "
"start of their contract."
msgstr ""
"Za razliko od |EOS| je rezervacija del plačilne liste zaposlenega od začetka "
"pogodbe."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:161
msgid ""
"Just like the |EOS|, the provision has two calculations depending on the "
"period spent by the employee in the company:"
msgstr ""
"Prav tako kot |EOS| ima rezervacija dva izračuna, odvisno od obdobja, ki ga "
"je zaposleni preživel v podjetju:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:164
msgid ""
"Less than 5 years: :math:`\\frac{\\text{Monthly Wage}}{30}\\times{\\frac{21}"
"{12}}`"
msgstr ""
"Manj kot 5 let: :math:`\\frac{\\text{Monthly Wage}}{30}\\times{\\frac{21}"
"{12}}`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:165
msgid ""
"More than 5 years: :math:`\\frac{\\text{Monthly Wage}}{30}\\times{\\frac{30}"
"{12}}`"
msgstr ""
"Več kot 5 let: :math:`\\frac{\\text{Monthly Wage}}{30}\\times{\\frac{30}{12}}"
"`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:168
msgid ""
"This rule is not shown to the employee on the payslip printout and it does "
"not affect their net payable, it is only for internal use by the company."
msgstr ""
"To pravilo ni prikazano zaposlenemu na izpisu plačilne liste in ne vpliva na "
"njegov neto znesek za izplačilo, namenjeno je samo interni uporabi podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:172
msgid "Annual leave provisions"
msgstr "Rezervacije za letni dopust"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:174
msgid ""
"Annual leave provisions are used for calculating the annual leave provision "
"accumulated each month, just like the |EOS| provision, it does not affect "
"the total amount paid to the employee, it is for internal use by the company."
msgstr ""
"Rezervacije za letni dopust se uporabljajo za izračun mesečno akumulirane "
"rezervacije za letni dopust, prav tako kot rezervacija |EOS|, ne vpliva na "
"skupni znesek, izplačan zaposlenemu, namenjena je interni uporabi podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:178
msgid ""
"It is calculated by dividing the employee's total salary (Total Salary = "
"Wage + Allowances) by **30** to get the daily salary. The daily salary is "
"then multiplied by the eligible leave days and divided by **12** to "
"determine the monthly provision amount."
msgstr ""
"Izračuna se tako, da se skupna plača zaposlenega (Skupna plača = Plača + "
"Dodatki) deli s **30**, da dobimo dnevno plačo. Dnevna plača se nato pomnoži "
"s številom upravičenih dni dopusta in deli z **12**, da določimo mesečni "
"znesek rezervacije."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:182
msgid ""
"\\text{Monthly Leave Provision} = \\frac{\\text{Total Salary} \\times "
"\\text{Number of Leave Days}}{30}\n"
"\\div 12"
msgstr ""
"\\text{Monthly Leave Provision} = \\frac{\\text{Total Salary} \\times "
"\\text{Number of Leave Days}}{30}\n"
"\\div 12"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:189
msgid "Social insurance contributions"
msgstr "Prispevki za socialno zavarovanje"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:191
msgid ""
"Social insurance contributions calculate the *social insurance*, which is "
"only available to |UAE| nationals."
msgstr ""
"Prispevki za socialno zavarovanje izračunajo *socialno zavarovanje*, ki je "
"na voljo samo državljanom |UAE|."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:194
msgid ""
"The company contributes **15%** of the total monthly salary for the employee "
"if the company is in **Abu Dhabi** and **12.5%** if the company is in "
"**another Emirate**."
msgstr ""
"Podjetje prispeva **15 %** skupne mesečne plače za zaposlenega, če je "
"podjetje v **Abu Dabiju**, in **12,5 %**, če je podjetje v **drugem "
"emiratu**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:198
msgid ""
"The total monthly salary for the employee = [basic + all allowances set on "
"the contract]."
msgstr ""
"Skupna mesečna plača za zaposlenega = [osnovna plača + vsi dodatki, določeni "
"v pogodbi]."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:200
msgid ""
"On the other hand, the employee contributes **5%** of their total monthly "
"salary and that amount gets deducted from the payslip amount."
msgstr ""
"Po drugi strani zaposleni prispeva **5 %** svoje skupne mesečne plače in ta "
"znesek se odšteje od zneska plačilne liste."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:204
msgid "Annual remaining leave balance rules"
msgstr "Pravila za preostalo stanje letnega dopusta"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:206
msgid ""
"Annual remaining leave balance rules are used for calculating the amount to "
"be paid to or taken from the employee based on the number of leave days "
"deserved by the employee during the current year."
msgstr ""
"Pravila za preostalo stanje letnega dopusta se uporabljajo za izračun "
"zneska, ki bo izplačan zaposlenemu ali odvzet od njega na podlagi števila "
"dni dopusta, do katerih je zaposleni upravičen v tekočem letu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:209
msgid ""
"The annual leave :doc:`time off type <../../time_off/time_off_types>` is "
"specified using the :guilabel:`Is Annual Leave` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Letni dopust :doc:`vrsta odsotnosti <../../time_off/time_off_types>` je "
"določen z uporabo potrditvenega polja :guilabel:`Je letni dopust`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:212
msgid ""
"If enabled, the rule calculates the amount of leave days deserved by the "
"employee up to the current date and subtracts the number of annual leave "
"days taken, and if the result is positive, this means that the employee "
"should be compensated for remaining amount and if negative this means that "
"the employee is liable to the company for the difference."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, pravilo izračuna količino dni dopusta, do katerih je "
"zaposleni upravičen do trenutnega datuma, in odšteje število porabljenih dni "
"letnega dopusta; če je rezultat pozitiven, to pomeni, da bi moral biti "
"zaposleni nadomestilo za preostali znesek, če pa je negativen, to pomeni, da "
"je zaposleni podjetju dolžan razliko."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:218
msgid "Sick leave rules"
msgstr "Pravila za bolniški dopust"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:220
msgid ""
"Sick leave rules provide the calculation for cases where the employee is on "
"sick leave and decides how the payslip should be affected."
msgstr ""
"Pravila o bolniški dopustni omogočajo izračun za primere, ko je kader na "
"bolniški odsotnosti, in določajo, kako naj bo plačilna lista prizadeta."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:223
msgid "There are **3 cases** for the employee to have:"
msgstr "Za kader obstajajo **3 primeri**:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:225
msgid ""
"**Fully paid sick leave:** The employee can upload a sick leave certificate "
"(SLI). Employees are eligible for **15 days** of this type of leave per "
"calendar year."
msgstr ""
"**Plačana bolniška dopustna:** Kader lahko naloži potrdilo o bolniški "
"odsotnosti (SLI). Kader je upravičen do **15 dni** te vrste dopusta na "
"koledarsko leto."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:229
msgid ""
"The SLI is not mandatory in Odoo but can be done from the setup of "
"the :doc:`time off types <../../time_off/time_off_types>`."
msgstr ""
"SLI v sistemu Odoo ni obvezen, vendar ga lahko nastavite pri "
"nastavitvi :doc:`tipov odsotnosti <../../time_off/time_off_types>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:232
msgid ""
"**50% paid sick leave:** Same as the fully paid one, but the employees are "
"eligible for **30 days** from this leave type. These 30 days are counted "
"after the first **15** fully paid days."
msgstr ""
"**50% plačana bolniška dopustna:** Enako kot polno plačana, vendar je kader "
"upravičen do **30 dni** te vrste dopusta. Teh 30 dni se šteje po prvih "
"**15** polno plačanih dneh."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:234
msgid ""
"**0% paid sick leave:** Same as the fully paid one, but the employees are "
"eligible for **45 days** from this leave type. These **45 days** are counted "
"after the first **15/30** fully/half-paid days."
msgstr ""
"**0% plačana bolniška dopustna:** Enako kot polno plačana, vendar je kader "
"upravičen do **45 dni** te vrste dopusta. Teh **45 dni** se šteje po prvih "
"**15/30** polno/delno plačanih dneh."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:239
msgid ""
"As per the labor law of the United Arab Emirates, the 15, 30, 45 days are "
"not specified as working days or calendar days so this point will rely on "
"the company policy."
msgstr ""
"Glede na delovno zakonodajo Združenih arabskih emiratov 15, 30, 45 dni niso "
"opredeljeni kot delovni dnevi ali koledarski dnevi, zato bo ta točka odvisna "
"od politike podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:242
msgid ""
"The amount paid for the employee per sick leave day is counted as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Znesek, plačan kadru na dan bolniške odsotnosti, se izračuna na naslednji "
"način:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:244
msgid ""
"\\frac{\\text{Number of Leave Days} \\times \\text{Gross Per Month}}{30} "
"\\times \\text{Percentage}"
msgstr ""
"\\frac{\\text{Število dni dopusta} \\times \\text{Bruto na mesec}}{30} "
"\\times \\text{Odstotek}"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:249
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:274
msgid ""
"Where the gross per month is the basic + all other allowances set on the "
"employee's contract."
msgstr ""
"Pri čemer je bruto na mesec osnova + vsi drugi dodatki, določeni v pogodbi "
"kadra."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:252
msgid "Daman investments end of service programme (DEWS)"
msgstr "Program odpravnine ob koncu službe Daman investments (DEWS)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:254
msgid ""
"|DEWS| allows for calculating the |DEWS| amounts for the employees who are "
"eligible for it and would like to be registered on it under their current "
"contract with the company."
msgstr ""
"|DEWS| omogoča izračun zneskov |DEWS| za kader, ki je upravičen do njega in "
"želi biti vpisan vanj v okviru svoje trenutne pogodbe s podjetjem."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:257
msgid ""
"It is calculated based on the number of years that employees have spent in "
"the company:"
msgstr ""
"Izračuna se na podlagi števila let, ki jih je kader preživel v podjetju:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:259
msgid ""
"**Less than 5 years:** 5.83% is deducted from the employee's **BASIC** "
"salary towards the DEWS."
msgstr ""
"**Manj kot 5 let:** 5,83 % se odšteje od **OSNOVNE** plače kadra za DEWS."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:260
msgid ""
"**More than 5 years:** 8.33% of The employee's **BASIC** is deducted from "
"the total payable for that employee."
msgstr ""
"**Več kot 5 let:** 8,33 % **OSNOVE** kadra se odšteje od skupne izplačila za "
"ta kader."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:264
msgid "Unpaid leaves"
msgstr "Neplačani dopusti"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:266
msgid ""
"Unpaid leaves allow for calculating the amount to be deducted when an "
"employee takes an unpaid leave. It is calculated by the following equation:"
msgstr ""
"Neoplačani dopusti omogočajo izračun zneska, ki ga je treba odšteti, ko "
"kader vzame neoplačan dopust. Izračuna se po naslednji enačbi:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:269
msgid ""
"\\frac{\\text{Total Number of Unpaid Leave Days} \\times \\text{Gross Per "
"Month}}{30}"
msgstr ""
"\\frac{\\text{Skupno število dni neplačanega dopusta} \\times \\text{Bruto "
"na mesec}}{30}"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:277
msgid "Out of contract days"
msgstr "Dnevi izven pogodbe"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:279
msgid ""
"The out of contract days rule provides a calculation for the days before/"
"after the contract period that overlaps with the contract of days on the "
"employee's payslips."
msgstr ""
"Pravilo o dneh izven pogodbe zagotavlja izračun za dneve pred/po obdobju "
"pogodbe, ki se prekriva z dnevniki pogodbe na plačilnih listah kadra."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:283
msgid ""
"Payslips are generated for the period of 1st-30th of September but the "
"contract expires on the 21st, in this case, there are 7 days flagged as out "
"of contract."
msgstr ""
"Plačilne liste se ustvarijo za obdobje od 1. do 30. septembra, vendar "
"pogodba preneha 21., v tem primeru je 7 dni označenih kot izven pogodbe."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:286
msgid "It is calculated by the following equation:"
msgstr "Izračuna se po naslednji enačbi:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:288
msgid ""
"\\frac{\\text{Total Number of Unpaid Leave Days} \\times \\text{Gross Per "
"Month}}{\\text{Number of Days in Current Month}}"
msgstr ""
"\\frac{\\text{Skupno število nenaplačanih dni dopusta} \\times \\text{Bruto "
"na mesec}}{\\text{Število dni v trenutnem mesecu}}"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:294
msgid "Manual deductions"
msgstr "Ročni odbitki"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:296
msgid ""
"Manual deductions allows the user to add manual deductions to be applied to "
"employees per payslip."
msgstr ""
"Ročni odbitki uporabniku omogočajo dodajanje ročnih odbitkov, ki se "
"uporabijo za kader na plačilno listo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:298
msgid ""
"The amount to be deducted and the description of the deduction is to be set "
"directly on the payslip manually as other inputs."
msgstr ""
"Znesek, ki naj se odbije, in opis odbitka je treba nastaviti neposredno na "
"plačilni listi ročno kot druge vnose."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:302
msgid "Net salary"
msgstr "Neto plača"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:304
msgid ""
"Net salary showcases the net amount that the employee will get based on the "
"payslip."
msgstr ""
"Neto plača prikazuje neto znesek, ki ga bo kader prejel na podlagi plačilne "
"liste."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:306
msgid ""
"It is calculated by adding basic to all allowances and deducting all "
"deductions from it."
msgstr ""
"Izračuna se tako, da se osnovi prištejejo vsi dodatki in se od tega "
"odtegnejo vsi odbitki."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:309
msgid ""
"The approach taken for the rules above is to first get the full amounts for "
"all static amounts that are set on the contract and then deduct the amounts "
"that should be deducted such as unpaid leaves, sick leaves, manual "
"deductions, commission, etc."
msgstr ""
"Pristop, uporabljen za zgornja pravila, je najprej pridobiti polne zneske za "
"vse statične zneske, ki so nastavljeni v pogodbi, nato pa odbiti zneske, ki "
"jih je treba odbiti, kot so nenaplačani dopusti, bolniški dopusti, ročni "
"odbitki, provizija itd."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:314
msgid "Employee net cost"
msgstr "Neto strošek kadra"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:316
msgid ""
"The employee net cost allows payroll officers to track the total employee "
"cost beyond the employee's net salary. The employee's net cost is computed "
"automatically upon each generated payslip and includes both direct and "
"indirect costs."
msgstr ""
"Neto stroški kadra omogočajo plačnim referentom spremljanje celotnih "
"stroškov kadra poleg neto plače kadra. Neto stroški kadra se izračunajo "
"samodejno ob vsakem ustvarjenem plačilnem listu in vključujejo neposredne "
"ter posredne stroške."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:320
msgid ""
"Direct costs represent the total amount payable to the employee, while "
"indirect costs include additional employer expenses, such as DEWS and social "
"insurance. Although these amounts are calculated and available in the system "
"for internal reporting and analysis, they do not appear on the payslip PDF "
"generated for the employee."
msgstr ""
"Neposredni stroški predstavljajo celoten znesek, ki se izplača kadru, medtem "
"ko posredni stroški vključujejo dodatne stroške delodajalca, kot so DEWS in "
"socialno zavarovanje. Čeprav so ti zneski izračunani in na voljo v sistemu "
"za interno poročanje in analizo, se ne pojavijo na PDF-ju plačilnega lista, "
"ustvarjenem za kader."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:326
msgid ""
"If an employee has a net payable salary of 20,000 AED, and the following "
"indirect costs:"
msgstr ""
"Če ima kader neto izplačljivo plačo 20.000 AED in naslednje posredne stroške:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:328
msgid "Medical insurance of 3,000 AED a year (250 AED a month)."
msgstr "Zdravstveno zavarovanje v višini 3.000 AED na leto (250 AED na mesec)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:329
msgid "Social Insurance Company Contribution of 3,000 AED."
msgstr ""
"Prispevek delodajalca za družbo za socialno zavarovanje v višini 3.000 AED."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:330
msgid "Social Insurance Employee Contribution 2,200 AED."
msgstr "Prispevek kadra za socialno zavarovanje 2.200 AED."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:332
msgid "The employee's Net Cost is: 20,000 + 250 + 3,000 + 2,200 = 23,250 AED"
msgstr "Neto stroški kadra so: 20.000 + 250 + 3.000 + 2.200 = 23.250 AED"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:335
msgid "Generating accounting entries from payslips"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje knjiženja iz plačilnih list"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:337
msgid ""
"The accounts are linked to each payroll rule as a debit or credit so that "
"when a draft entry is generated from a payslip, the amounts are reflected on "
"the accounts accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Računi so povezani z vsakim pravilom plačnega seznama kot breme ali dobro, "
"tako da ko se iz plačilne liste ustvari osnutek knjiženja, so zneski "
"ustrezno odraženi na računih."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:340
msgid ""
"The accounts need to be set in a way that would make the end-result entry "
"balanced, otherwise a warning is raised if it is not balanced and it will "
"not generate the entry."
msgstr ""
"Račune je treba nastaviti tako, da bo končni rezultat knjiženja uravnotežen, "
"sicer se pojavi opozorilo, če ni uravnotežen, in knjiženje se ne bo "
"ustvarilo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:343
msgid ""
"After reviewing the payslips and making sure that all the amounts are "
"correct, generate a draft entry, either one entry for all employees or an "
"entry per employee depending on the setup done on the settings."
msgstr ""
"Po pregledu plačilnih list in preverjanju, da so vsi zneski pravilni, "
"ustvarite osnutek knjiženja – eno knjiženje za vse kadre ali knjiženje za "
"vsakega kadra posebej, odvisno od nastavitev v nastavitvah."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:348
msgid "Debit and credit accounts set up for the basic and allowance rules."
msgstr ""
"Bremenski in dobroimetni računi, nastavljeni za osnovna pravila in pravila "
"dodatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid "Accounting setup for the rules."
msgstr "Računovodske nastavitve za pravila."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:354
msgid "Pay employees"
msgstr "Plačaj zaposlene"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:356
msgid ""
"After a batch or a payslip's journal entry has been posted, the company can "
"proceed to pay their employees."
msgstr ""
"Ko je knjiženje serije ali plačilne liste objavljeno, lahko podjetje "
"nadaljuje s plačilom svojega kadra."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:359
msgid ""
"In the batch itself or on the payslip, by clicking on the pay button, a "
"payment is created and linked to the posted entry for the payslip. The same "
"can be done for batch payslips if one payment is done from a single/multiple "
"payment bank/cash journal."
msgstr ""
"V sami seriji ali na plačilni listi s klikom na gumb za plačilo se ustvari "
"plačilo in se poveže z objavljenim knjiženjem za plačilno listo. Enako je "
"mogoče storiti za plačilne liste v seriji, če se opravi eno plačilo iz enega "
"ali več bančnih/gotovinskiških dnevnikov plačil."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:364
msgid ""
"Once the payslip is generated, the employee will be able to access the slips "
"from their portal users. They will automatically receive an email mentioning "
"that the payslips are now available to be viewed on their portal view."
msgstr ""
"Ko je plačilna lista ustvarjena, bo kader lahko dostopal do listov iz svojih "
"portalskih uporabnikov. Samodejno bodo prejeli e-pošto z obvestilom, da so "
"plačilne liste zdaj na voljo za ogled v njihovem portalskem pogledu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:369
msgid "Payslip printouts"
msgstr "Izpisi plačilnih list"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:371
msgid ""
"Two printout formats can be extracted from the payslip depending on the "
"*type* of payslip, either a *Monthly* payslip or an *End of Service* "
"Payslip. It is triggered if the employee the payslip is generated for was "
"archived during that month."
msgstr ""
"Iz plačilnega lista je mogoče izvleči dve obliki izpisa, odvisno od *vrste* "
"plačilnega lista, bodisi *mesečni* plačilni list bodisi plačilni list ob "
"*prenehanju službe*. Sproži se, če je bil kader, za katerega je bil "
"ustvarjen plačilni list, arhiviran v tem mesecu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:376
msgid "Instant Pay structure"
msgstr "Struktura takojšnjega plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:378
msgid ""
"This structure is used when off-cycle payslips are required to make payments "
"to employees for special situations, such as one-time or advance salaries. "
"Examples of one-time payments include:"
msgstr ""
"Ta struktura se uporablja, kadar so potrebne izvendavkovčne plačilne liste "
"za izvajanje plačil kadru za posebne situacije, kot so enkratne ali "
"predplačila plač. Primeri enkratnih plačil vključujejo:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:382
msgid "Bonuses"
msgstr "Bonusi"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:383
msgid "Allowances"
msgstr "Nadomestila"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:386
msgid "Salary Advances"
msgstr "Akontacije plač"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:388
msgid ""
"Employees may request a portion of their salary before the end of the pay "
"cycle. In such cases, the payroll officer can issue a salary advance using "
"the following steps:"
msgstr ""
"Kadri lahko zaprosijo za del svoje plače pred koncem plačilnega cikla. V "
"takih primerih lahko referent za plače izda akontacijo plače po naslednjih "
"korakih:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:391
msgid ""
"Create an off-cycle payslip using the United Arab Emirates: Instant Pay "
"structure."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite plačilni listek izven cikla z uporabo strukture Združeni arabski "
"emirati: takojšnja izplačila."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:393
msgid ""
"Add another input of type Salary Advance and specify the amount to be paid "
"to the employee."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte še en vnos tipa Akontacija plače in določite znesek, ki naj se "
"izplača kadru."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:395
msgid "Confirm the payslip and process the payment."
msgstr "Potrdite plačilni listek in obdelajte plačilo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:397
msgid ""
"In the next cycle, when a payslip is generated for the employee using the "
"`United Arab Emirates: Regular Pay` structure, another input type, `Advance "
"Recovery`, is automatically added for the same amount that was previously "
"paid."
msgstr ""
"V naslednjem ciklu, ko je za kader ustvarjen plačilni list z uporabo "
"strukture `Združeni arabski emirati: Redna plača`, se samodejno doda še ena "
"vrsta vnosa, `Vračilo predplačila`, za isti znesek, ki je bil predhodno "
"izplačan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:402
msgid ""
"If the employee and payroll officer agree to recover the advance over two "
"consecutive cycles, the payroll officer can adjust the Advance Recovery "
"amount on the first payslip. The remaining balance is automatically added to "
"the following cycle."
msgstr ""
"Če se kader in referent za plače dogovorita, da se akontacija povrne v dveh "
"zaporednih ciklih, lahko referent za plače prilagodi znesek Vračilo "
"akontacije na prvem plačilnem listku. Preostalo stanje se samodejno doda v "
"naslednji cikel."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:409
msgid "Wages protection system (WPS) reports"
msgstr "Poročila sistema za zaščito plač (WPS)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:411
msgid ""
"The |WPS| is a report that needs to be submitted by the company to prove "
"that they paid their employees the right amounts on the right dates. It can "
"either be generated per payslip or batch."
msgstr ""
"|WPS| je poročilo, ki ga mora podjetje predložiti kot dokaz, da je svojim "
"kadrom izplačalo pravilne zneske na pravilne datume. Ustvari se lahko za "
"posamezen plačilni listek ali serijo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:414
msgid "The following steps need to be followed before generating the report:"
msgstr "Pred ustvarjanjem poročila je treba slediti naslednjim korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:416
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Payroll --> Configuration --> Settings` and under "
"the :guilabel:`Emirati Localization` section, configure the following:"
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Plačni seznam --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` "
"in v razdelku :guilabel:`Emiratska lokalizacija` konfigurirajte naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:419
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employer Unique ID`: Set a unique identifier for the company to "
"be used in the |WPS| report."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Edinstvena ID delodajalca`: Nastavite edinstveni identifikator "
"podjetja, ki se bo uporabljal v poročilu |WPS|."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:421
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salaries Bank Account`: Select a bank account or start typing "
"to :guilabel:`Create and edit` a new bank account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bančni račun za plače`: Izberite bančni račun ali začnite "
"tipkati, da :guilabel:`Ustvarite in uredite` nov bančni račun."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:425
msgid ""
"When setting the :guilabel:`Salaries Bank Account` make sure to complete the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Pri nastavljanju :guilabel:`Bančnega računa za plače` poskrbite, da "
"izpolnite naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:427
msgid ":guilabel:`Account Holder`: set as the company."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Imetnik računa`: nastavite kot podjetje."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:428
msgid ":guilabel:`Account Number`: has to be a valid IBAN."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Številka računa`: mora biti veljaven IBAN."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:429
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank`: has to have the :guilabel:`Routing Code Agent` set and "
"consist of a 9-digit numeric value only."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Banka`: mora imeti nastavljen :guilabel:`Koda usmerjanja agenta` "
"in vsebovati le 9-mestno numerično vrednost."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:431
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Send Money`: should be enabled and set to :guilabel:`Trusted`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pošiljanje denarja`: mora biti omogočeno in nastavljeno "
"na :guilabel:`Zaupanja vredno`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:433
msgid ""
"Set the unique identifier on all of the employees who are a part of the "
"target of the batch/payslip."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite edinstveni identifikator za vse kadre, ki so del ciljne serije/"
"plačilnega listka."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:436
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Identification No` field can be found on the employee's page "
"under the :guilabel:`Personal` tab."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Identifikacijska številka` najdete na strani kadra v "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Osebno`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:439
msgid ""
"Once the initial setup is done, the |WPS| can be generated either for one "
"payslip or for a batch as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je začetna nastavitev opravljena, se |WPS| ustvari za en plačilni listek "
"ali za serijo na naslednji način:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:442
msgid "Generate the payslip one by one or as a batch."
msgstr "Ustvarite plačilne listke enega za drugim ali kot serijo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:443
msgid "Post the draft entity related to the payslips."
msgstr "Objavite osnutek entitete, povezane s plačilnimi listami."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:444
msgid ""
"Create the payment report and set the :guilabel:`Export Format` "
"to :guilabel:`UAE WPS`."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite poročilo o plačilu in nastavite :guilabel:`Obliko izvoza` "
"na :guilabel:`UAE WPS`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:447
msgid ""
"The Report can either be exported in a .sif format or a .xslx, as they both "
"have the same format."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo je mogoče izvoziti v formatu .sif ali .xslx, saj imata oba enak "
"format."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:449
msgid "The resulting file consists of the following:"
msgstr "Nastala datoteka je sestavljena iz naslednjega:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:451
msgid ""
"**Employee Detail Record** (**EDR**): includes details of the employees on "
"the batch. There should be one :abbr:`EDR (Employee Detail Record)` record "
"per employee."
msgstr ""
"**Zapis s podrobnostmi o kadru** (**EDR**): vključuje podrobnosti o kadrih v "
"paketni obdelavi. Za vsakega v kadru mora biti en zapis :abbr:`EDR (Employee "
"Detail Record)`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:453
msgid ""
"**Employee Variable Pay** (**EVP**): includes the details of the variable "
"salary the employee got on that payslip. If the employee has any. The "
"variable amounts are calculated from when other inputs are used that are "
"linked to the salary rules (:menuselection:`Payroll --> Configuration --> "
"Rules`)."
msgstr ""
"**Spremenljiva plača kadra** (**EVP**): vključuje podrobnosti o spremenljivi "
"plači, ki jo je kader prejel na tem plačilnem listu, če jo ima. Spremenljivi "
"zneski se izračunajo, ko se uporabijo drugi vnosi, ki so povezani s pravili "
"plač (:menuselection:`Plačni seznam --> Konfiguracija --> Pravila`)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:457
msgid ""
"**Salary Control Record** (**SCR**): There should only be one :abbr:`SCR "
"(Salary Control Record)` per |WPS| file as it indicates the employer details "
"and the totals for the payslips."
msgstr ""
"**Nadzorni zapis plač** (**SCR**): Za vsako datoteko |WPS| mora biti samo "
"en :abbr:`SCR (Salary Control Record)`, saj prikazuje podrobnosti "
"delodajalca in skupne zneske za plačilne liste."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:461
msgid ""
"The exported format is based on MoHRE guidelines and is aligned with the "
"formats used by most WPS agents in the United Arab Emirates, including "
"Emirates NBD, Emirates Islamic Bank, First Abu Dhabi Bank (FAB), and Dubai "
"Islamic Bank (DIB), among others."
msgstr ""
"Izvoženi format temelji na smernicah MoHRE in je usklajen s formati, ki jih "
"uporablja večina agentov WPS v Združenih arabskih emiratih, vključno z "
"Emirates NBD, Emirates Islamic Bank, First Abu Dhabi Bank (FAB) in Dubai "
"Islamic Bank (DIB) ter drugi."

